  "synopsis": "He's bald. He's bad. His lightsaber is purple. He's Mace Windu! Make sure not to miss out on this stunning tribute to the baddest Jedi Council member to ever have his midi-chlorians counted! Featuring \"The Secret of Tet-Ami\" by Fabian Nicieza and Timothy II, \"Children of the Force\" by Jason Hall and Lucas Marangon, \"The Sith in Shadow\" by Bob Harris and Jerome Opena, and much more! Featuring a cover by Tim Bradstreet!",
